# CHANGELOG - APPEND ONLY
# Object: registry-freeze-protocol

## v1.0 (2025-02-23)
### Initial Release

#### Added
- Registry state model (BOOTSTRAP/FROZEN/HOTFIX/DEPRECATED)
- Pre-freeze checklist (P0/P1 gates)
- Freeze process workflow (5 steps)
- Emergency unfreeze process (hotfix only)
- T3C/Hace enable gate control
- Compliance monitoring (filesystem watch, seal verification)
- Violation handling protocols
- .FROZEN marker file format
- Snapshot management strategy
- Pre-freeze testing suite
- Post-freeze operation rules
- Metrics & KPI tracking

#### Why
- Ngăn chặn registry mutation sau production
- Gate control trước khi enable T3C/Hace
- Emergency hotfix capability với governance
- Đảm bảo seal integrity không bị phá vỡ
- Audit trail cho mọi state transition

#### Dependencies
- constitution/seal-integrity-law.clo (pending)
- constitution/override-precedence-law.clo (pending)
- rule/append-only-registry-rule.clo [LOCKED]
- rule/deterministic-build-rule.clo (pending)

#### Compliance
- Follows AIL v3.1.8 (85% VI + 15% EN)
- Fractal naming: ros.protocol.registry.freeze
- Lazy type: gate_control_protocol
- Core Four governance model

#### Testing Required Before Seal
- Deterministic load test (100 runs)
- Seal integrity verification
- Authority boundary enforcement
- Hotfix flow simulation
- Performance benchmark (< 100ms)
